item.title: SoftLayer_Ticket_Update_Employee
item.description: SoftLayer_Ticket_Update_Employee Service Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Ticket_Update_Employee data type models an update to a ticket made by a SoftLayer employee. Local createDate The data a ticket update was created. Type: dateTime editorId The internal identifier of the SoftLayer portal or API user who created a ticket update. This is only used if a ticket update's ''editorType'' property is "USER". Type: integer
